*Installation of herafitter is easy if "fink" is installed:

export CERN_ROOT=/sw/
* the following are neede for running with kt-factorision option:
export QCDNUM_ROOT=/Users/jung/jung/cvs/qcdnum/qcdnum-17-00-04
export CASCADE_ROOT=/Users/jung/jung/cvs/cascade2
export PYTHIA_ROOT=/Volumes/genser-light/MCGenerators/pythia6/425

./configure


* to compile qcdnum, add the follwoing in all makelibs, include: 
ar -s ../lib/.....
